data.description: 2 Story home nestled in the highly coveted Green Valley Ranch, this corner lot treasure is eagerly awaiting your arrival. Surrounded by mature trees, it offers unparalleled beauty and seclusion. Vast living space ideal for hosting and entertainment. The heart of this home is its recently updated kitchen—a haven for culinary aficionados. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or hosting vibrant gatherings on the expansive back yard deck, set against the backdrop of a generous backyard. The basement is tastefully completed with 2 bedrooms and ¾ bath with a bonus room.  The upper floor bonus room is a haven for remote work or tranquil relaxation. Its open layout radiates a welcoming vibe, it will blossom into the home of your dreams.  Perfectly situated near schools, parks, shops, and dining, its location is unbeatable. This is your chance to secure a sought-after gem in Green Valley Ranch—don't delay, as this opportunity won't last!
